	  when CRL is not present in chain. Merged patch by Michal Witkowski.
	  Closes Bug 405233.
	* storage_ldapvcard rebind like auth_ldap for successful connection
	  to MS Active Directory as LDAP storage. Merged patch by x0r.
	  Closes Bug 532367

