    * sx/sx.h: same

    * c2s/main.c: use sx_raw_write() to send keepalives (closes #3144)
    * c2s/c2s.c: same
    * c2s/c2s.h: same
    * s2s/main.c: same
    * s2s/out.c: same
    * s2s/s2s.h: same

    * sm/pkt.c: treat empty packet addresses as though they don't exist

